dct_title_s: Map of the Yellowstone and Missouri Rivers and their tributaries
dct_description_sm: Shows railroads, trails and routes. Relief shown by hachures. At head of title: War Department. Includes list of authorities. Western sheet published in 1877.
dct_creator_sm: United States. Army. Office of the Chief of Engineers
dct_publisher_sm: [Washington, D.C.] : Published by authority of the Hon. the Secretary of War, Office of the Chief of Engineers, U.S. Army, 1876.
